[
    {
        "text": "Humans once wielded formidable magical power.",
        "source": "api",
        "start_time": 0.0,
        "end_time": 0.0,
        "start_progress": 0.06784734347717636,
        "end_progress": 0.06784734347717636
    },
    {
        "text": "But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect.",
        "source": "api",
        "start_time": 0.0,
        "end_time": 0.0,
        "start_progress": 0.06784734347717636,
        "end_progress": 0.06784734347717636
    },
    {
        "text": "When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.",
        "source": "api",
        "start_time": 0.0,
        "end_time": 0.0,
        "start_progress": 0.06784734347717636,
        "end_progress": 0.06784734347717636
    },
    {
        "text": "Quite frankly, it's a little unsettling!",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 0.0,
        "end_time": 13.0,
        "start_progress": 0.06809678223996009,
        "end_progress": 0.07807433275130955
    },
    {
        "text": "This is because Mana causes people to change into monsters.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 13.0,
        "end_time": 33.0,
        "start_progress": 0.0783237715140933,
        "end_progress": 0.09304065851833375
    },
    {
        "text": "The story follows the adventures of a young man named Takuma who has been transformed into a monster.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 33.0,
        "end_time": 42.0,
        "start_progress": 0.09329009728111748,
        "end_progress": 0.11873285108505861
    },
    {
        "text": "He has been given the ability to transform back into his human form for a short time, but only if he can consume enough Mana to do so.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 42.0,
        "end_time": 50.0,
        "start_progress": 0.11923172861062609,
        "end_progress": 0.1526565228236468
    },
    {
        "text": "He is joined by a young woman named Elvy who has the same condition.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 50.0,
        "end_time": 56.0,
        "start_progress": 0.15290596158643052,
        "end_progress": 0.1698677974557246
    },
    {
        "text": "It's unfortunate because becoming a monster is really the only defense that humans have against the hostile aliens.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 56.0,
        "end_time": 87.0,
        "start_progress": 0.17011723621850836,
        "end_progress": 0.19880269393863806
    },
    {
        "text": "Yet at the same time, it's a curse because it makes them look like monsters to their fellow humans.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 87.0,
        "end_time": 105.0,
        "start_progress": 0.1990521327014218,
        "end_progress": 0.22374657021701172
    },
    {
        "text": "Of course, no human wants to look like a monster.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 105.0,
        "end_time": 112.0,
        "start_progress": 0.22399600897979546,
        "end_progress": 0.23621850835619856
    },
    {
        "text": "Monsters are ugly and scary, and they're not very popular.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 112.0,
        "end_time": 124.0,
        "start_progress": 0.23646794711898228,
        "end_progress": 0.250935395360439
    },
    {
        "text": "So Takuma and Elvy really have their work cut out for them.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 124.0,
        "end_time": 133.0,
        "start_progress": 0.25118483412322273,
        "end_progress": 0.2659017211274632
    },
    {
        "text": "They need to find Mana, but they also need to find a way to hide their condition from the other humans.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 133.0,
        "end_time": 147.0,
        "start_progress": 0.26615115989024696,
        "end_progress": 0.2918433524569718
    },
    {
        "text": "They don't want to be seen, because if other humans see monsters among them, it will cause a panic.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 147.0,
        "end_time": 164.0,
        "start_progress": 0.29209279121975557,
        "end_progress": 0.3167872287353455
    },
    {
        "text": "So Takuma and Elvy must be very careful.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 164.0,
        "end_time": 175.0,
        "start_progress": 0.3170366674981292,
        "end_progress": 0.32701421800947866
    },
    {
        "text": "They try to stay hidden, but they also need to find Mana.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 175.0,
        "end_time": 182.0,
        "start_progress": 0.32726365677226243,
        "end_progress": 0.3414816662509354
    },
    {
        "text": "If they don't, they'll never be able to return to their human forms.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 182.0,
        "end_time": 191.0,
        "start_progress": 0.3417311050137191,
        "end_progress": 0.35869294088301323
    },
    {
        "text": "Takuma and Elvy are joined by a young man named Shion who has also been transformed into a monster.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 191.0,
        "end_time": 211.0,
        "start_progress": 0.35894237964579695,
        "end_progress": 0.38413569468695435
    },
    {
        "text": "He's a little older than Takuma, but he's also a bit of a troublemaker.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 211.0,
        "end_time": 216.0,
        "start_progress": 0.38438513344973807,
        "end_progress": 0.4020952856073834
    },
    {
        "text": "Because of his troublemaker status, he's been kicked out of his home, and he's on the run.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 216.0,
        "end_time": 228.0,
        "start_progress": 0.4023447243701671,
        "end_progress": 0.4247942130207034
    },
    {
        "text": "Shion is a little bit of a rebel, and he's not very good at following orders.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 228.0,
        "end_time": 234.0,
        "start_progress": 0.42504365178348713,
        "end_progress": 0.44425043651783486
    },
    {
        "text": "This makes Takuma and Elvy very nervous.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 234.0,
        "end_time": 248.0,
        "start_progress": 0.44449987528061863,
        "end_progress": 0.4544774257919681
    },
    {
        "text": "In order to survive, they need to stick together, but Shion doesn't seem to understand this.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 248.0,
        "end_time": 263.0,
        "start_progress": 0.4547268645547518,
        "end_progress": 0.47767523073085555
    },
    {
        "text": "Shion repeatedly tries to leave the group, and he's always getting into trouble.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 263.0,
        "end_time": 275.0,
        "start_progress": 0.4779246694936393,
        "end_progress": 0.49787977051633825
    },
    {
        "text": "Takuma finally has enough, and he decides to teach Shion a lesson.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 275.0,
        "end_time": 283.0,
        "start_progress": 0.49812920927912197,
        "end_progress": 0.5145921676228485
    },
    {
        "text": "He tells Shion that he needs to be the one to get the Mana.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 283.0,
        "end_time": 291.0,
        "start_progress": 0.5148416063856324,
        "end_progress": 0.5295584933898728
    },
    {
        "text": "Takuma says that if Shion can't do it, then he should just leave.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 291.0,
        "end_time": 317.0,
        "start_progress": 0.5298079321526565,
        "end_progress": 0.5460214517335994
    },
    {
        "text": "Shion is shocked that Takuma would say such a thing, but Takuma tells him that he's just being honest.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 317.0,
        "end_time": 329.0,
        "start_progress": 0.5462708904963831,
        "end_progress": 0.5717136443003242
    },
    {
        "text": "Shion decides to take Takuma up on his challenge.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 329.0,
        "end_time": 336.0,
        "start_progress": 0.5719630830631081,
        "end_progress": 0.5841855824395111
    },
    {
        "text": "He 's going to get the Mana, and he's going to prove that he's not a loser.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 336.0,
        "end_time": 342.0,
        "start_progress": 0.5844350212022948,
        "end_progress": 0.6031429284110751
    },
    {
        "text": "Takuma is impressed by Shion's determination, and he decides to help him.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 342.0,
        "end_time": 348.0,
        "start_progress": 0.6033923671738588,
        "end_progress": 0.6216013968570716
    },
    {
        "text": "Takuma and Elvy will help Shion get the Mana.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 348.0,
        "end_time": 352.0,
        "start_progress": 0.6218508356198553,
        "end_progress": 0.6330755799451234
    },
    {
        "text": "The three of them set out on a journey to find the Mana.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 352.0,
        "end_time": 358.0,
        "start_progress": 0.6333250187079073,
        "end_progress": 0.6475430281865802
    },
    {
        "text": "They travel to a place called the \"Mana Zone\" where the Mana is supposed to be the most concentrated.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 358.0,
        "end_time": 364.0,
        "start_progress": 0.6480419057121477,
        "end_progress": 0.6732352207533051
    },
    {
        "text": "They hope to find enough Mana to transform back into humans.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 364.0,
        "end_time": 372.0,
        "start_progress": 0.6734846595160888,
        "end_progress": 0.688450985283113
    },
    {
        "text": "But they also need to be careful because the Mana Zone is also home to the hostile aliens.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 372.0,
        "end_time": 380.0,
        "start_progress": 0.6887004240458967,
        "end_progress": 0.711149912696433
    },
    {
        "text": "The aliens are very dangerous, and they will attack anyone who enters the Mana Zone.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 380.0,
        "end_time": 385.0,
        "start_progress": 0.7113993514592167,
        "end_progress": 0.7323522075330506
    },
    {
        "text": "So, in the quiet of the night, Takuma, Elvy, and Shion sneak into the Mana Zone.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 385.0,
        "end_time": 396.0,
        "start_progress": 0.7326016462958344,
        "end_progress": 0.7525567473185333
    },
    {
        "text": "They hope to find the Mana before the aliens find them.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 396.0,
        "end_time": 406.0,
        "start_progress": 0.752806186081317,
        "end_progress": 0.7665253180344226
    },
    {
        "text": "Shion is the one who spots the Mana first.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 406.0,
        "end_time": 420.0,
        "start_progress": 0.7667747567972063,
        "end_progress": 0.7772511848341233
    },
    {
        "text": "It's a small glowing ball of light, and it's floating in the air.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 420.0,
        "end_time": 426.0,
        "start_progress": 0.777500623596907,
        "end_progress": 0.7937141431778498
    },
    {
        "text": "Shion is so excited that he tries to grab it.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 426.0,
        "end_time": 433.0,
        "start_progress": 0.7939635819406335,
        "end_progress": 0.8051883262659018
    },
    {
        "text": "But the Mana is very elusive, and it keeps flying away.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 433.0,
        "end_time": 437.0,
        "start_progress": 0.8054377650286855,
        "end_progress": 0.819156896981791
    },
    {
        "text": "Takuma and Elvy try to help Shion, but they can't seem to catch it either.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 437.0,
        "end_time": 444.0,
        "start_progress": 0.8194063357445747,
        "end_progress": 0.8378648041905712
    },
    {
        "text": "It's as if the Mana is playing a game with them.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 444.0,
        "end_time": 450.0,
        "start_progress": 0.8381142429533549,
        "end_progress": 0.8500873035669743
    },
    {
        "text": "The Mana is very fast, and it's very tricky.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 450.0,
        "end_time": 460.0,
        "start_progress": 0.8503367423297581,
        "end_progress": 0.8613120478922425
    },
    {
        "text": "Takuma and Elvy are surprised by how much trouble they're having.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 460.0,
        "end_time": 468.0,
        "start_progress": 0.8615614866550262,
        "end_progress": 0.877775006235969
    },
    {
        "text": "Finally, they manage to corner the Mana.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 468.0,
        "end_time": 475.0,
        "start_progress": 0.8780244449987528,
        "end_progress": 0.8880019955101023
    },
    {
        "text": "They grab onto it, and they pull it down to the ground.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 475.0,
        "end_time": 480.0,
        "start_progress": 0.888251434272886,
        "end_progress": 0.9019705662259915
    },
    {
        "text": "Shion quickly snatches it up, and he puts it in his pocket.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 480.0,
        "end_time": 489.0,
        "start_progress": 0.9022200049887753,
        "end_progress": 0.9169368919930158
    },
    {
        "text": "Takuma and Elvy are relieved.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 489.0,
        "end_time": 499.0,
        "start_progress": 0.9171863307557995,
        "end_progress": 0.9244200548765278
    },
    {
        "text": "The three monsters have finally captured the Mana.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 499.0,
        "end_time": 508.0,
        "start_progress": 0.9246694936393115,
        "end_progress": 0.9371414317784984
    },
    {
        "text": "They split the Mana into three equal parts, and they each take one.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 508.0,
        "end_time": 524.0,
        "start_progress": 0.9373908705412821,
        "end_progress": 0.9541032676477925
    },
    {
        "text": "One by one, they start to transform back into humans.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 524.0,
        "end_time": 550.0,
        "start_progress": 0.9543527064105762,
        "end_progress": 0.9675729608381143
    },
    {
        "text": "They are relieved to see that the aliens that have been attacking them have all been killed off by their fellow monsters as well!",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 550.0,
        "end_time": 585.0,
        "start_progress": 0.967822399600898,
        "end_progress": 1.0
    }
]